    "name": "Street Food Simulator",
    "steam_appid": 3330840,
    "required_age": 0,
    "is_free": false,
    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >&quot;Street Food Simulator&quot; 是一款第一人称模拟游戏，让你可以从容地管理街头小吃摊的每一个细节。</p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >完美烤制</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >掌握烧烤的艺术！提供美味、完美烹饪的食物来满足顾客的食欲。把握每道菜的时间，让所有顾客都满意。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/19fdbc5aa46bb1c8571c3fef856148ee.poster.avif?t=1766247532\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/19fdbc5aa46bb1c8571c3fef856148ee.webm?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/19fdbc5aa46bb1c8571c3fef856148ee.mp4?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >寻找城市中的最佳位置</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >探索城市，发现人群聚集的理想地点。最大化你的销售额，让你的餐车成为城市中的热门去处。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/466f6066e6104fa224d71c286b3d0f00.poster.avif?t=1766247532\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/466f6066e6104fa224d71c286b3d0f00.webm?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/466f6066e6104fa224d71c286b3d0f00.mp4?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >自定义你的餐车</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >在市场上查看各种餐车，并根据你的喜好进行自定义。购买冰箱、收音机、烤架等设备。通过不同的油漆颜色让餐车焕然一新。努力脱颖而出，在城市中留下深刻的印象。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/3f1656e1ea379d3d96d6bb56f8fc3f2f.poster.avif?t=1766247532\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/3f1656e1ea379d3d96d6bb56f8fc3f2f.webm?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/3f1656e1ea379d3d96d6bb56f8fc3f2f.mp4?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >竞争对手</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >击败你的竞争对手，他们各自拥有独特的技能和经营方式。他们在城市的不同区域经营，拥有不同的策略和优势。了解他们的差异将帮助你获得竞争优势，超越他们并主宰市场。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/564057dcd5dffa23364c657267a5cb1f.poster.avif?t=1766247532\" width=800 height=452 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/564057dcd5dffa23364c657267a5cb1f.webm?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/564057dcd5dffa23364c657267a5cb1f.mp4?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >成长</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >通过迎接新的挑战、增加菜单菜品、吸引忠实顾客来扩展你的街头美食帝国，让成功不断增长。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/c9e7a6f2e7661d1c2a0bb25a0fbaf66e.poster.avif?t=1766247532\" width=640 height=360 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/c9e7a6f2e7661d1c2a0bb25a0fbaf66e.webm?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/3330840/extras/c9e7a6f2e7661d1c2a0bb25a0fbaf66e.mp4?t=1766247532\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\" >开发路线图</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >《Street Food Simulator》是一款抢先体验游戏，未来还会有更多内容推出。我们计划每月更新。计划添加的主要功能包括： </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >来自不同国家的更多本地街头美食。</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >新的城市和城镇可供探索与发展。</p></ul><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p>",
